        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
        <img src="./asset/image/turning-points-a-journey-through-challenges kalam.webp" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="Turning Points:">Turning Points:</h5>
          <p class="card-text">Turning Points is the sequel to Wings of Fire, covering his life until 1992. This book chronicles his administration and the events that occurred during it. The book is more of a Vision 2020 roadmap.
           </p>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Click here</a>
